The image of the idyllic island from afar is breathtakingly beautiful. The sun is setting in the background, painting the sky in shades of orange, pink and purple. The sea is a mesmerizing shade of blue, with gentle waves that lap against the shore. The sandy beach is pristine and stretches out for miles.
